title: Bikini model gets an incident proposal after taking to streets to ask strangers to fund her boob job
text:
News Bikini model gets an incident proposal after taking to streets to ask strangers to fund her boob job Even this Norwegian beauty didn't expect that offer as she stood on London's South Bank where onlookers dug deep, whistled and even took her to task Share Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now The 'boob job' money is actually for breast cancer charity Share this video Get daily   Thank you for subscribing!   
The say models are demanding, but one bikini-clad beauty stood on London's South Bank asking STRANGERS to fund her boob job. 
But even she got the shock of her life when one bloke tried his luck by saying he'd give her £1,000 towards the £5,000 target - but only if he got to spend the night with her. 
The indecent proposal came as Juliane Snekkestad’s brazen request sparked some interesting reactions from passers by as she stood holding a sign reading 'Model: Need money for boob job'. 
Many asked for selfies with the Norwegian now based in London, while others dropped donations into the cup - including a plucky little boy. Bikini model gets a little bit of cash from this lucky lad on South Bank (Photo: YouTube/DengisV) While a lot of people simply got selfies with the Norwegian model (Photo: YouTube/DengisV) 
Some women dug deep, while others just laughed and one guy whistled at Juliane. 
However a female passerby criticised her for wanting to alter her body at all by telling the model: "It’s not about image, it’s about what’s in you and expressing that and not something that’s only on your body." Read More Kendall Jenner bares bum for Mario Testino V magazine cover as she reveals battle with anxiety 
The cheekiest moment came from a lad, whose identity was not revealed on camera, who asked Juliane how much she needed to raise. 
When she told him her target was £5,000 he replied: "I’ll give you a grand for a night with me. To help you out." The model gets an incident proposal from one cheeky passerby (Photo: YouTube/DengisV) 
Unsurprisingly, all was not as it seemed. 
The blonde beauty had no real intention of ever going under the knife. 
She was doing it as part of a prank orchestrated by YouTube jokers DengisV and Jasonmoments.
